{
  "stem": "25938.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that uprising.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People weren't-- you heard about Himmler?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They made a deal with someone that they'll stop sending, and they stopped.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] too much, I think.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I read about that, that the [? last ?] [? couple-- ?] even from the Red Cross, we got food the last few-- you remember in Dachau, we had food.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was different, see?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had food from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Remember, we had sugar.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people died from-- they ate sugar too much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It affected their stomach.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How do you know it came from the Red Cross?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They told-- we knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We talked about that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know, but people talked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They heard that from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I read that, too, after the war, about--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes there are contradictions.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what to believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the point is, now in my mind, there's that rumor that was from the Red Cross.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know how-- if I-- if I-- if I talked about that in Dachau, or maybe after the war.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the air that the war was-- that they're going to lose the war because we were [INAUDIBLE] the march.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The death march.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- I was in that march, I and my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they evacuated us because the [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "American ?] army, the Allies came already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were near Berlin.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We're on the road, we know because they evacuated the guards, because-- they evacuated the camp and themselves.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They couldn't stay.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was near the front.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The front is-- we knew that.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
